different populations. And finally,

00:03:06.170 --> 00:03:12.260
Admixture mapping. This is an approach to
find the genes that determine differences

00:03:12.260 --> 00:03:17.960
between populations. When we have those
genes, we can then use them to design more

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:23.160
experiments to help us understand better
